title: Dachshund joy reunited with squeaky toy after five years
text: Share this article Share When he posted the video online Mr Lowell Simpson captioned it: 'Finn reunites with his favourite toy after nearly five years. 'When he was just a few months old he had a toy pig but destroyed it. 'He went through a few pigs before we upgraded to more durable toys.' The dog's joy at being reunited is obvious, and he squeals with happiness at the sound of ever squeak. Finn's joy at being reunited is obvious and he squeals with happiness at the sound of ever squeak His ecstatic reaction at being reunited with his toy quickly went rival with one viewer describing it as 'pure joy' The video of Finn quickly went viral after it was posted on YouTube on Sunday, quickly gaining more than 300,000 views. Viewers were smitten with Finn and his love for his toy. One wrote: 'Pure joy.' Another added: 'This is just the most adorable thing.' Share or comment on this article 8
